  lines:
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\u201C...The warmth... I haven\u2019t felt it in so long. You brought
      it back. You brought us back.\u201D\n\n[He looks around as other villagers
      begin to stir, emotions washing over him.]"
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\u201CWe were fading\u2026 one by one, into silence and stone. But you...
      you\u2019ve returned the light.\u201D\n[He walks toward the tree, placing a
      hand gently on its bark.]\n"
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\u201CThough the village lives again, this tree... it\u2019s only a fragment.
      A branch, connected to something far greater \u2014 the World Sun Tree. \u201CAnd
      that great tree... is dying. I can feel it. Its light dims more each day, and
      with it, so does the light in every corner of our world.\u201D\n"
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: '"there is not much time, they are coming back.."


      [Turns back to
      you, his tone now more serious.]'
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\u201CThat shard you carry - its not just light, its a seed form the tree
      I can feel there conection its full of life. you must take it to the higter
      islands there you may uncover the truth.\"\n\n[He looks to the mountains beyond
      the village.]"
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\"you must travel upward \u2014 to the higher island, where the Tower
      Keepers still guard the old ways. There, you may learn more.\u201D\n\n[Points
      to a platform nearby, now faintly glowing.]"
  - speakerName: village elder
    text: "\u201CAfter you're gone... we may turn to stone once more. But for now,
      you've given us warmth, light... and hope.  We will wait for your return\""
